&lt;figure&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;code-area&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;line-numbers language-bash&#34; data-language=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34;&gt;man gh
GH(1)                                                   GitHub CLI manual                                                   GH(1)

NAME
       gh - GitHub CLI

SYNOPSIS
       gh &amp;lt;command&amp;gt; &amp;lt;subcommand&amp;gt; [flags]

DESCRIPTION
       Work seamlessly with GitHub from the command line.

CORE COMMANDS
       gh-auth(1)
              Authenticate gh and git with GitHub

       gh-browse(1)
              Open the repository in the browser

       gh-codespace(1)
              Connect to and manage your codespaces

       gh-gist(1)
              Manage gists

       gh-issue(1)
              Manage issues

       gh-pr(1)
              Manage pull requests

       gh-release(1)
              Manage releases

       gh-repo(1)
